               </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p>Intraduisible.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p>Not usefully translatable.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p>Intraducibile.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p>غير قابل للترجمة بشكل جيد</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>This fragmentary letter might be the left half of a zeta or the lower half of an eta, depending on the orientation.</p>
                <p>This letter, standing by itself or followed by others, may be the beginning of a name or a trademark, perhaps with the numerical value of 7. 
                Nothing may be decided.</p>
                <p/>
            </div></body>
